Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:12.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就没有什么能把高木同学吓得尖叫的办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:19.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,总之 像这样每天都被她捉弄的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.29,0:00:21.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:28.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:30.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:33.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:35.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:37.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:41.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一起去学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:44.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:19.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比身高
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:23.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:26.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,刚才被她看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:28.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:29.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:32.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要一起骑车去学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:34.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:36.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被发现的话会挨骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:38.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是不好意思才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:40.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:41.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:47.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看来我撞上电线杆的事情没被她看到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:53.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片也终于换长袖了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:58.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最近变冷了 感觉差不多该换了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:01.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:03.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你长个了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:08.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,春天的时候感觉你的制服比现在宽松一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:10.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:16.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,现在有种「制服 is 正义」的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:20.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道我到发育期了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:27.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 最近一个劲地长个子 真难办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道到了发育期吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:33.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学倒是没感觉有什么变化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:40.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你这可是性骚扰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:43.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,居然说没变化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:46.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:50.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不是这个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:53.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说的是身高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我在说身高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:58.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你以为我在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:08.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:15.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉你还是没怎么长高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不不 长高了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:21.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,说不定我现在比高木同学还要高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:26.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那来比比身高吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:35.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么要来这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,穿着鞋子比不出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,小心迟到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:42.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,马上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,来 背对背站好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:54.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:58.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉好暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:09.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一般不都是轮流贴着墙壁作记号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,两个人背对着量更准嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,应该差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:20.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:24.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,来嘛 西片也来确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:32.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我没说错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:37.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你没垫脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:40.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 你居然怀疑我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:42.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,0:05:50.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,面对面的话 就算垫脚也会知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:55.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个 那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:07.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉好像我要高一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:09.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为我刚才垫脚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:13.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你果然垫脚了啊 大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:16.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可没有说过我没垫脚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:19.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了 终于赢过我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:23.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个高木同学 一副从容的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:26.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,心里肯定很不甘心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:31.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还有 我没有不甘心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:35.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为要是块头变大的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就会撞上电线杆 很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:49.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看到了吗 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:51.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,走吧 去学校啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:56.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说 高木同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:09.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有那么冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:15.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉很怕冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:16.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:19.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈 你手好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:27.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怕冷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:33.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再这样干我可饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:43.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你们的手为什么那么冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:46.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,手冷的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:52.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,内心很温暖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:56.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我觉得内心很温暖的人不会做刚才那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:59.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好了好了 别那么记仇嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:04.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你再干的话我真的要生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:06.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你明明已经生气了好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:12.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 不要啊早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这是心暖攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,救命啊 由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:22.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这是刚才的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:29.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉的手 好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但她的心拔凉拔凉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:34.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么会这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:37.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好冷啊 不要靠过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:39.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,心寒攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:40.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,走为上策
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:41.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:42.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你也可以摸回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:58.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好冷啊好冷啊 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:08:59.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:06.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我怎么可能会这样干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:13.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都叫你住手了 好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:17.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,手冷的人 内心是暖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪里暖了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木和西片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:27.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天一起上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,关系真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,他们果然在交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:43.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片和高木在交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:45.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:47.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,他们关系特别好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:51.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉 你很羡慕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:54.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 因为嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,与其说是羡慕…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:10:01.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈 由加莉说想和男生唧唧我我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:03.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我才没这样说过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:05.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈 你在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:08.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:11.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要突然跟我搭话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:14.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,本来快要尿出来的 现在尿不出来了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:18.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早苗真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:20.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个很有趣的 去看看比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:22.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的吗 我会看的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:23.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:31.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想到了很厉害的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:34.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,如果是这个犀利的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:36.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,放学的时候肯定能捉弄到高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在偷笑什么呢 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:47.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好猥琐喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:49.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我才没有想那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:51.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那种事情是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:52.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:54.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你脸好红
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:57.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,给我走着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说回来 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:03.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:12.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好 难道她发觉我在设计她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:17.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:19.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么你要再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:22.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:27.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,放学时你说不定还会改变主意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以的话到时候再给我答复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:33.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:40.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她究竟怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算了 反正不被发觉就行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:44.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:48.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天来我家玩超级大乱斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:48.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7}原文スパプラ，应该是山寨明星大乱?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:53.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉 今天不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:56.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么啊 又要陪女朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:57.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:59.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是高木同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:01.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哈？你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,根本就不是那回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:06.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木和西片没在交往哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:09.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我刚才在厕所听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:11.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:11.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,突然想去小便了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:17.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,厕所…厕所…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:21.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那家伙刚才在厕所干什么去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:26.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:27.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然你们没在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:30.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那为什么你会和高木同学一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:32.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个嘛 因为被她邀请了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这不就是因为在交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:36.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:40.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,应该不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:44.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,下节课要去实验室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好 赶紧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:13:01.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 我觉得高木同学只是想捉弄我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:05.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:08.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天不可以绕远路了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:13.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想吃椪柑冰棍 我想吃椪柑冰棍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:15.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大冷天的还吃什么冰棍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:18.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在被炉吃冰棍超棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:19.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:23.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「给我答复」也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:27.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要我重新邀请她的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:31.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉有点不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:35.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我还没邀请过她一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:36.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:38.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:42.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了 高木同学来问我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:43.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我只要说个Yes就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:49.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天有人问我是不是在和西片交往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:55.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然后 我好像被认为是喜欢西片的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:14:00.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是不是因为总是我在邀请你一起回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原来这就是你的目的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:09.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,创造出让我来邀请你的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:13.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然后取笑我害羞的反应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:15.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:18.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要强装平静
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:20.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「哼 这样啊」这样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:25.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,诶 原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.47,0:14:26.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:30.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说回来 关于早上的答复
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:38.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,反正我没什么事 一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:42.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:44.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,加油啊我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只要跨过了这一关
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:50.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就能捉弄到高木同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:57.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一起回家怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么办好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:09.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,开玩笑的 回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:12.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:18.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片好像还有什么计划的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:20.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暴露了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:29.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然暴露了 那还是不要做比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:33.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但我好不容易想出来的点子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:37.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说我还完全没想过要怎样弄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要不要买果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:48.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉喉咙干干的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大部分都卖完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:57.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明想喝冷饮的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:58.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,剩下的只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:00.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,红豆汤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:03.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还有猎奇的饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:03.23,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs120\pos(918,330)\frz3.238}艾草汁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:03.23,Takagisan-huamian-1,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fs50\pos(1164,702)}西瓜味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:08.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉无论选哪个都会后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:11.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,无论选哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:15.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要去别的自动贩卖机看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:20.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我喉咙也渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:23.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,总之先…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:32.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好难喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看包装就能猜到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:38.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,钱白花了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:40.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:42.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样一来就能开始我的计划了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:44.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:51.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好喝的热饮和难喝得要命的饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪个比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:02.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,二选一问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:08.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好喝但是烫手的饮料和难喝得要命的饮料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么样啊高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难以选择吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:13.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你就犯难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:16.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,让我看看你为难的表情 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:18.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:23.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是我喝了好喝的热饮发烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:25.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片会来探望我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:30.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这有什么关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:31.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,关系大着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:34.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:39.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然发烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:42.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我应该会去探望你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:44.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我选好喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:47.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:50.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦 真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:53.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这是什么感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:56.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学完全没有为难嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:18:02.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不如说为难的是我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:05.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,二选一问题的作战失败了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:09.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不 放弃还为之过早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:10.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那下一题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:12.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:16.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是选一辈子没有零花钱呢 还是不再捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:17.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一辈子没有零花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:18.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:24.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为我有压岁钱作积蓄 暂时没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:26.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到了高中只要打工就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:30.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以还是选捉弄西片比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我太小瞧高木同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:35.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,得问些更刁钻的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:36.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:39.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,从刚才开始你就在问些奇怪的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道说 你想让我为难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:49.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没 没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:52.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我也要提问了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:58.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不在和被我捉弄一辈子 哪个比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:00.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不在是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:09.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,虽然我也不想被她捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:12.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但消失什么的…那也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:15.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那 我选被你捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:20.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你果然喜欢被捉弄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:23.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才没有 肯定是讨厌被捉弄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:28.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不太希望你消失…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:32.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也就是说 你想一辈子和我在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:36.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你脸好红哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:39.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:42.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,让我发窘就这么有意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:45.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也得问个好问题才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:46.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么下一题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:48.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 还要继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:53.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一辈子考零分 以及和我接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:54.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪个比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接…接…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:02.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪个比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:05.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,考零分 看了书也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:07.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 无论干什么都是零分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:10.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:14.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样的话不仅以后肯定拿不到零花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:15.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,甚至连高中也上不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:20.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但要选了接吻的话 肯定会被她捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:22.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你很纠结嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:23.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:26.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我越纠结 高木同学她就越开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:29.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,得赶紧作出选择
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:31.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,零分太残酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:32.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:34.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:37.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那 那就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:39.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,选不是考零分那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:41.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是考零分的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:47.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接 接吻的那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:10.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:14.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片的个子要高一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:17.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了西片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:20.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我在比身高而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:35.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到头来又被狠狠地捉弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:40.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是我学到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:43.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其中一个选项一定要是选不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:46.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只要另一个是捉弄用的选项
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:48.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这场对决就能稳赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:50.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学 下一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:51.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么下一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:56.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,倒立着绕校园走一圈和两个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:59.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,稍微等一下 我不会倒立
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:02.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说还轮不到我提问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:04.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,首先要回答我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.26,0:22:05.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 你看…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:50.07,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:54.49,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:01:04.79,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:13.63,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}校庭で君のことを一番に見つけて今日は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.67,0:01:21.89,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて話しかけようか？ ちょっと考えるの楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:24.85,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風に揺らされるカーテン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:30.23,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不意打ちに当たる日差し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:34.15,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しそうな顔を笑ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:38.03,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}照れて伏せちゃうのね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:46.16,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}憂鬱なテストも吹き飛ばせるような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:54.42,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ、二人で秘密の約束をしたいなって提案です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:59.84,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:03.85,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:14.11,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:50.07,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}会错意了也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:54.49,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 这样想着却不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:01:04.79,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}弥漫在周围的那阵幽香 想在你的身边静静感受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:13.63,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在校园的庭院 第一个发现你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.67,0:01:21.89,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今天要和你说些什么呢 即便是想着这些也是一种乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:24.85,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窗帘随风起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:30.23,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不经意地投入一束阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:34.15,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那美丽的容颜笑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:38.03,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}羞得我抬不起头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:46.16,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}风儿喧嚣 似要吹散考试的忧郁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:54.42,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}呐 我想要和你一起 立下两人的秘密约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:59.84,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}会错意了也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:03.85,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 这样想着却不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:14.11,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}弥漫在周围的那阵幽香 想在你的身边静静感受
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:15.69,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}広い宇宙の数ある一つ　青い地球の広い世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.69,0:22:24.65,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}小さな恋の思いは届く　小さな島のあなたのもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:30.70,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}あなたと出会い　時は流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:35.37,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}思いをこめた　手紙もふえる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:40.29,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}いつしか二人互いに響く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.34,0:22:45.01,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}時に激しく　時に切なく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:49.68,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}響くは遠く　遥か彼方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:54.43,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}優しい歌は　世界を変える
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.94,0:23:01.23,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ほら　あなたにとって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:07.24,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}大事な人ほど　すぐそばにいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:13.37,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ただあなたにだけ　届いて欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:16.75,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}響け恋の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:25.71,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ほら　ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:34.76,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ほら　響け恋の歌
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:15.69,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}想把这辽阔宇宙中绝无仅有的小小的相思之情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.69,0:22:24.65,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}传达给蔚蓝地球上广阔世界中小小岛屿上的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:30.70,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}与你邂逅 光阴飞逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:35.37,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}饱含思念的信件堆积如山
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:40.29,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不知不觉我们心生共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.34,0:22:45.01,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}时而充满激情 时而伤感不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:49.68,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}回响渐渐远去 到那遥远彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:54.43,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那温柔的歌声 改变了我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.94,0:23:01.23,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你看 对你而言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:07.24,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}重要的人近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:13.37,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}只愿你能感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:16.75,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}这响彻天地的恋歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:25.71,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你听 你听
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:31.05,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}听见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:34.76,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}这响彻天地的恋歌
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——STAFF——
